.SH "NAME"
.sp
limelight
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fBlimelight\fP [\fB\-v\fP,\fB\-\-version\fP|\fB\-V\fP,\fB\-\-verbose\fP|\fB\-m\fP,\fB\-\-message\fP \fImsg\fP|\fB\-c\fP,\fB\-\-config\fP \fIconfig_file\fP]
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
\fBlimelight\fP is a port of the window borders implementaion that used to be in yabai.
.SH "OPTIONS"
.sp
\fB\-v\fP, \fB\-\-version\fP
.RS 4
Print the version and exit.
.RE
.sp
\fB\-V\fP, \fB\-\-verbose\fP
.RS 4
Output debug information to stdout.
.RE
.sp
\fB\-m\fP, \fB\-\-message\fP \fI<msg>\fP
.RS 4
Send message to a running instance of limelight.
.RE
.sp
\fB\-c\fP, \fB\-\-config\fP \fI<config_file>\fP
.RS 4
Use the specified configuration file.
.RE
.SH "DOMAINS"
.SS "Config"
.SS "General Syntax"
.sp
limelight \-m config <setting>
.RS 4
Get or set the value of <setting>.
.RE
.SS "Settings"
.sp
\fBdebug_output\fP [\fIon|off\fP]
.RS 4
Enable output of debug information to stdout.
.RE
.sp
\fBplacement\fP [\fIexterior|interior|inset\fP]
.RS 4
Position/draw\-mode of window border.
.RE
.sp
\fBwidth\fP [\fI<integer number>\fP]
.RS 4
Width of window borders.
.RE
.sp
\fBradius\fP [\fI<floating point number>\fP]
.RS 4
Radius of window border corners.
.RE
.sp
\fBactive_color\fP [\fI<0xAARRGGBB>\fP]
.RS 4
Color of the border of the focused window.
.RE
.sp
\fBnormal_color\fP [\fI<0xAARRGGBB>\fP]
.RS 4
Color of the border of an unfocused window.
.RE
.SH "EXIT CODES"
.sp
If \fBlimelight\fP can\(cqt handle a message, it will return a non\-zero exit code.
